\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Step 1: Story & Introduction\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs24 \cf0 You want the app/website to start with a little story about 
\f3\i who Kailia is
\f2\i0 .\uc0\u8232 
\f4 \uc0\u55357 \u56393 
\f2  We can write a short, engaging intro \'97 maybe Kailia is a magical character (like a friendly guide) who takes the kids on learning adventures.\
Think: 
\f1\b \'93Kailia lives in a colorful world where words, numbers, and stories come alive! She needs your help on her adventures. To join her, let\'92s see where you are in your journey!\'94
\f2\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 Step 2: Developmental Age Assessment\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs24 \cf0 You\'92ll need a short, 
\f1\b evidence-based screening tool
\f2\b0  to figure out where the child is developmentally (instead of just chronological age).\
The most used, short, parent-friendly tools are:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Ages & Stages Questionnaire (ASQ-3)
\f2\b0  
\f5 \uc0\u8594 
\f2  widely used, 1\'9666 months (up to 5 years). But it\'92s not free.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 CDC Milestone Checklists
\f2\b0  
\f5 \uc0\u8594 
\f2  FREE, easy, covers birth\'965 years (basic version, but not comprehensive for older kids).\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Wide Range Achievement Test (WRAT)
\f2\b0  
\f5 \uc0\u8594 
\f2  screens reading, spelling, and math skills (for older children, 5\'9612).\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Free alternative approach:
\f2\b0  You can design your own 
\f1\b mini \'93placement test\'94
\f2\b0  with a few fun questions per domain (reading, writing, communication, math). This way you\'92re not locked into licensing fees.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f4 \cf0 \uc0\u10145 \u65039 
\f2  For your app, the practical option is a 
\f1\b fun placement quiz
\f2\b0  that feels like a game:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \'93Can you match these letters with sounds?\'94\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \'93Can you count how many apples Kailia has?\'94\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 \'93Can you draw a line to connect the word with the picture?\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 That way, the app gets a baseline without needing an official test (which often requires licensing).\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
